  "title": "Do Not The Snack",
  "description": "Make specified pokemon not be spawnable by poke snacks",
  "body": "<div><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/8494ec1ac495cfb481dc7e458356325510933eb0/assets/cozy/supported/neoforge_vector.svg\" alt=\"Available For NeoForge\" height=\"56\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/8494ec1ac495cfb481dc7e458356325510933eb0/assets/cozy/supported/fabric_vector.svg\" alt=\"Available For Fabric\" height=\"56\"> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/do-not-the-snack\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\" alt=\"Available On Modrinth\" height=\"56\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/do-not-the-snack\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\" alt=\"Available On CurseForge\" height=\"56\"></a><br><a href=\"https://discord.gg/dVPqq2U4xy\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-singular_vector.svg\" alt=\"discord-singular\" height=\"56\"></a> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/milosworks\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/kofi-singular_vector.svg\" alt=\"kofi-singular\" height=\"56\"></a></div>\n\nThis mod is very simple, it simply allows you to make pokemon defined in the config file or , just add the species of the pokemon in the `ignoredPokemon` array, just like this:\n\n`donotthesnack-server.toml` on neoforge `ignored_pokemon = [ \"pikachu\", \"smeargle\", \"bidoof\" ]`\n\n`donotthesnack.json` on fabric `{ \"ignoredPokemon\": [ \"pikachu\", \"smeargle\", \"bidoof\" ] }`\n\n_If this mod has helped you in any way, consider donating to my ko-fi on the top of the description, thank you so much!_",
